OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy across the west with
OL,6,Foccasional rain, this may turn more
OL,7,Fpersistent at times this afternoon
OL,8,Fespecially along the west coast. Dry
OL,9,Felsewhere, some bright spells breaking
OL,10,Fthrough along the Moray coast. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with rain at times
OL,13,Facross the west, heavy at times. Drier
OL,14,Facross the east with a few clear
OL,15,Fperiods in the northeast. Mild.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FLittle change, further rain
OL,18,Fat times in the west and north,
OL,19,Fbecoming more widespread by evening.
OL,20,FDrier in the east with a little
OL,21,Fbrightness. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
