OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FShowers or longer spells of rain on
OL,7,FThursday. Colder on Friday with
OL,8,Fshowers, these mainly in the west.
OL,9,FFurther rain expected on Saturday.
